metadata.name: STOP
metadata.description:
What does "Stunningly Sensual Woman" mean?
It is a gift, a prize, a happiness for the man who is lucky enough to meet her.  She is very emotional and lives with an open heart and soul. When a sensual woman is happy, her soul rejoices in ecstasy. When she is unhappy her soul sings.
Excerpt from the song "Stop" by singer Sam Brown.
